# A [[markup]] language that is used by the [[MediaWiki]] [[software]]; thus, it is in general use in [[wiki]]s.  Some examples of wiki markup are the use of double brackets to create intermal links (<nowiki>[[Link location|link title]]</nowiki>).  Wiki markup is specially designed for use in an encyclopedia, and is also designed to be easy to use.